history.content:
Dear Students,

The CS Advisors are available today for one last drop-in day this semester, 10-12PM & 1-4PM in 349 Soda. 
Starting Friday, December 20th at 12PM, we will be unavailable for appointments and drop-in through January 10th, so that we can focus on administrative projects. 
**We will still be available via email during this time, so please contact us at cs-advising@cs.berkeley.edu.**
 
Appointments will resume on Monday, January 13th; drop-in advising will resume on Wednesday, January 15th, 10-12PM & 1-4PM in 349 Soda.
 
Best of luck with finals!! 
CS Advisors
